elements.name: Check Contract from RTD_CONTRACT where STATUS is DONE

steps.name: Select Contract from Table in DB with Query "SELECT RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.KTP,RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.CONTRACT_ID,RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.RECIPIENT_BANK_ACCOUNT_NUMBER,RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.STATUS FROM RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP LEFT JOIN RTD_CONTRACT ON RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.CONTRACT_ID=RTD_CONTRACT.CONTRACT_ID WHERE RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.TYPE_CONTRACT='MPF' AND RTD_CONTRACT.STATUS=11 AND RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.IS_RTD='Y' AND RTD_CONTRACT.PGW_RESPONSE_CODE='00'"

arguments.val: SELECT RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.KTP,RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.CONTRACT_ID,RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.RECIPIENT_BANK_ACCOUNT_NUMBER,RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.STATUS FROM RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP LEFT JOIN RTD_CONTRACT ON RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.CONTRACT_ID=RTD_CONTRACT.CONTRACT_ID WHERE RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.TYPE_CONTRACT='MPF' AND RTD_CONTRACT.STATUS=11 AND RTD_CONTRACT_TEMP.IS_RTD='Y' AND RTD_CONTRACT.PGW_RESPONSE_CODE='00'
